cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.GR

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with image and video processing, specifically style transfer of facial expressions and attributes.
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses improvements in adversarial training, which is a popular technique in machine learning.
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with automated extraction of shared attributes from unaligned video frames.
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with video processing and transformation.
5. cs.GR (Graphics) is also a possible category as the paper deals with generating transformation videos with improved consistency and stability.
